---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import fishboneImg from '../../assets/fishbone.png';
---

<MainLayout title="Fishbone Analysis">
    <section class="space-y-10">
        <header class="max-w-4xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-600 mb-3">
                Initiation
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Fishbone Analysis
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                The fishbone (Ishikawa) diagram below maps the root causes of vandalism to Rand Water
                infrastructure and highlights key contributing factors.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <img  src={fishboneImg.src}  width={fishboneImg.width}  height={fishboneImg.height}  alt="Fishbone analysis"/>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-500">
                Figure: Root cause analysis of vandalism affecting water infrastructure.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</MainLayout>